## Running the Brain

```bash
neurogrim score --registry .claude/brain-registry.json
neurogrim narrate --hat visionary --registry .claude/brain-registry.json

# Run code-side sensory tools:
neurogrim sensory test-health --project-root . > .claude/test-health-cmdb.json
neurogrim sensory code-quality --project-root . > .claude/code-quality-cmdb.json
neurogrim sensory deploy-readiness --project-root . > .claude/deploy-readiness-cmdb.json
```

## Cultural substrate

`.claude/culture.yaml` is byte-identical to the canonical LSP Brains
federation copy. Five invariants ŌĆö `positivity`, `integrity`, `honesty`,
`critical_but_kind`, `respect` ŌĆö applied as a floor.

## The PostToolUse hook

`.claude/settings.local.json` (gitignored) wires the PostToolUse hook
recording every Skill invocation to `.claude/brain/invocation-ledger.jsonl`.

## What agents working here should know

1. **Two surfaces, one Brain.** Code domains roll up to scoring; abstract
   domains observe state until operators promote them.
2. **Promote abstract domains via spec ┬¦15.5 discipline.** Calibration
   audit + ledger entry; not casual.
3. **Cultural substrate applies after hats and human-comms.**

